{"tid":1091553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光頭漢大圍車廂偷拍裙底春 乘客職員合力制服","createTime":"2019-04-04T08:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T09:58:58.000Z","uid":29627,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"74eddfc30a345bd90ef5953837f28a735658d979","tid":1091553,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"光頭漢大圍車廂偷拍裙底春 乘客職員合力制服<br />\n<br />\n早上8時許上班繁忙時間，港鐵大圍車廂發生偷拍裙底春事件，疑人被到場警員拘捕。一名光頭男疑在車廂中偷拍一位女乘客裙底，被其他乘客發現，欲上前逮住他，惟光頭男激烈反抗，有兩名見義勇為的男乘客不忿色狼行為將他按住，過程被乘客拍下上載社交網站，片中可見乘客向色狼喝令：「唔好反抗呀！唔好郁！」對方則大叫「冇呀」，按着他的乘客回應：「你冇就唔駛驚吖，冇咪畀人睇（電話）囉！」未幾便見有港鐵職員接報到達車廂了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n讀者何先生當時正由大圍站上車，準備到火炭站上班，他在大圍站月台見到有5名港鐵職員圍住一名光頭男，他聽到有乘客指光頭男涉嫌偷拍裙底，「見到有電話放喺地下，個男人本來坐喺度，突然間走開擒欄杆想跳落去，職員即衝上前喺咁捉住佢，然後㩒低佢。其實欄杆底下係樓梯，都好高㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n從何先生拍得的片段可見，當時疑人情緒激動，衝向欄杆，一隻腳已跨上欄欲跳下，被5名港鐵職員合力制止拉回，並將他按倒地上，大叫「唔好郁」，稍後數名警員接報趕至，向疑人盤查。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，早上8時29分，港鐵職員報案，指大圍站發生疑偷拍裙底案件，警員到場調查，44歲女子懷疑遭59歲姓馬男子，以手機偷拍裙底，警方拘捕馬涉嫌破壞公眾體統，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190404/large/1554350498_4124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190404%2Flarge%2F1554350498_4124.jpg&h=97fd9904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊女事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190404/59448149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59448149&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=d0280a10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59448149&h=665a28ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190404/59448149</a>"},{"pid":"fbf104bf878d9aa7670c7c1eaefd42733ac28275","tid":1091553,"uid":113335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/cb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9/tumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fcb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9%2Ftumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif&h=7127c8ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc364a378e68e65258ef1ba86a8ada65bb81f673","tid":1091553,"uid":58201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fbf104bf878d9aa7670c7c1eaefd42733ac28275","tid":1091553,"uid":113335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/cb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9/tumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fcb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9%2Ftumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif&h=7127c8ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚似MING仔"},{"pid":"7c74952d1aea4e75634301b6e17566232113e810","tid":1091553,"uid":174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf104bf878d9aa7670c7c1eaefd42733ac28275","tid":1091553,"uid":113335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/cb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9/tumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fcb8f5fe843ffcb4ecc3b2627f6eba8c9%2Ftumblr_oiy9ojtAjJ1qaijwvo1_400.gif&h=7127c8ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:31:21.000Z","msg":"咩劇嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7d228dad496699091f11de2e1bde69b8fe5fd2","tid":1091553,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc364a378e68e65258ef1ba86a8ada65bb81f673","tid":1091553,"uid":58201,"like":4,"disli